TITLE: Upsert Operation Using 'unless conflict' in EdgeQL
DESCRIPTION: This EdgeQL query demonstrates an upsert operation, attempting to insert a Movie object and updating it if a conflict occurs on the title field.
SOURCE: https://github.com/geldata/gel/blob/master/docs/reference/edgeql/insert.rst#2025-04-16_snippet_6

LANGUAGE: edgeql
CODE:
```
with
  title := "Eternals",
  release_year := 2021
insert Movie {
  title := title,
  release_year := release_year
}
unless conflict on .title
else (
  update Movie set { release_year := release_year }
);
```

