TITLE: Generating OpenAI Chat Completion Answer in TypeScript
DESCRIPTION: This function sends a request to the OpenAI chat completion API with the prepared prompt. It configures the model, maximum tokens, temperature, and enables streaming of the response.
SOURCE: https://github.com/geldata/gel/blob/master/docs/resources/guides/tutorials/chatgpt_bot.rst#2025-04-16_snippet_37

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
async function getOpenAiAnswer(prompt: string) {
  const completion = await openai.chat.completions
    .create({
      model: "gpt-3.5-turbo",
      messages: [{ role: "user", content: prompt }],
      max_tokens: 1024,
      temperature: 0.1,
      stream: true,
    })
    .asResponse();

  return completion;
}
```

