TITLE: Comparing Full-text Search with Trigram Word Similarity Search in EdgeDB
DESCRIPTION: This example demonstrates the difference between full-text search and trigram matching. When searching for a misspelled term 'thaco', the full-text search fails, but the trigram word similarity search succeeds because the term is close enough to the actual acronym 'THAC0'.
