TITLE: Computed Links with Same Title Query
DESCRIPTION: Shows how to create a computed link that returns all movies with the same title using a dynamic query.
SOURCE: https://github.com/geldata/gel/blob/master/docs/intro/schema.rst#2025-04-16_snippet_7

LANGUAGE: sdl
CODE:
```
type Movie {
  required title: str;
  multi actors: Person;

  # returns all movies with same title
  multi same_title := (
    with t := .title
    select detached Movie filter .title = t
  )
}
```

