TITLE: JavaScript Transaction API Example
DESCRIPTION: Shows how to use the new transaction API in the JavaScript client binding, including nested transactions with savepoints.
SOURCE: https://github.com/geldata/gel/blob/master/docs/resources/changelog/1_0_a5.rst#2025-04-16_snippet_3

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
await con.transaction(async () => {
    await con.execute(`
        insert Example {
            name := 'Test Transaction 1'
        };
    `);
    await con.execute("select 1 / 0;");
});

// nested transactions are supported
// and handle save points
await con.transaction(async () => {

    // nested transaction
    await con.transaction(async () => {
        await con.execute(`
            insert Example {
                name := 'Test Transaction 2'
            };
        `);
    });
});
```

