TITLE: Importing Bookmark Data from JSON to EdgeDB
DESCRIPTION: This Python script demonstrates how to import Bookmark data from a JSON dump into EdgeDB by updating User objects with multi-link data.
SOURCE: https://github.com/geldata/gel/blob/master/docs/resources/guides/datamigrations/postgres.rst#2025-04-16_snippet_12

LANGUAGE: python
CODE:
```
for line in open('bookmarks.json'):
    client.query('''
        with data := to_json(<str>$line)
        update User
        filter .app_id = <int32>data['user_id']
        set {
            bookmark += (
                select Post {
                    @note := <str>data['note']
                }
                filter .app_id = <int32>data['post_id']
            ),
        }
    ''',
    line=line)
```

