TITLE: Deleting Single Book with Complex Filtering
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates deleting a single book using author filter, sorting, and limit constraints
SOURCE: https://github.com/geldata/gel/blob/master/docs/reference/using/graphql/mutations.rst#2025-04-16_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: graphql
CODE:
```
mutation delete_one_book {
    delete_Book(
        filter: {
            author: {
                name: {
                    eq: "Lewis Carroll"
                }
            }
        },
        order: {
            title: {
                dir: ASC
            }
        },
        first: 1
    ) {
        title
        synopsis
    }
}
```

LANGUAGE: edgeql
CODE:
```
select (
    delete Book
    filter
        Book.author.name = 'Lewis Carroll'
    order by
        Book.title ASC
    limit 1
) {
    title,
    synopsis
};
```

