TITLE: Selecting All Properties with Spread Operator in Gel TypeScript
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates how to use the '*' property and spread operator as a shorthand for selecting all properties of a given object type.
SOURCE: https://github.com/geldata/gel/blob/master/docs/reference/using/js/querybuilder.rst#2025-04-16_snippet_56

