TITLE: Changing Admin Password for Gel Instance
DESCRIPTION: Uses gel query to change the password for the admin role of the Gel instance, utilizing the previously set IP and PASSWORD variables.
SOURCE: https://github.com/geldata/gel/blob/master/docs/reference/running/deployment/digitalocean.rst#2025-04-16_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: bash
CODE:
```
$ printf gelpassword | gel query \
         --host $IP \
         --password-from-stdin \
         --tls-security insecure \
