LANGUAGE: sdl
CODE:
```
type User {
    # Make sure user names are unique.
    required name: str {
        constraint exclusive;
    }
    # Already indexed, don't need to do this:
    # index on (.name)

    # Make sure none of the "owned" items belong
    # to any other user.
    multi owns: Item {
        constraint exclusive;
    }
}
```

