TITLE: Querying User Data with Nested Select in EdgeQL
DESCRIPTION: This snippet demonstrates a select statement that retrieves user data along with their owned issues. It uses a nested select to fetch related data and applies a filter on the user's name.
SOURCE: https://github.com/geldata/gel/blob/master/docs/reference/reference/edgeql/select.rst#2025-04-16_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: edgeql
CODE:
```
with module example
select User {
    name,
    owned := (select
        User.<owner[is Issue] {
            number,
            body
        }
    )
}
filter User.name like 'Alice%';
```

