TITLE: Multiple Parameter Grouping
DESCRIPTION: Groups movies by multiple parameters (vowel start and decade) demonstrating complex grouping patterns.
SOURCE: https://github.com/geldata/gel/blob/master/docs/reference/reference/edgeql/group.rst#2025-04-16_snippet_4

LANGUAGE: edgeql
CODE:
```
with
  M := (select Movie filter .release_year > 2015),
  groups := (
    group M {title}
    using
      vowel := re_test('(?i)^[aeiou]', .title),
      decade := .release_year // 10
    by vowel, decade
  )
select groups {
  key := .key {vowel, decade},
  count := count(.elements),
  mean_title_length :=
    math::mean(len(.elements.title))
};
```

