TITLE: Insert or Update Person Using Unless Conflict in EdgeQL
DESCRIPTION: Shows how to use the unless conflict clause to either insert a new Person object or update an existing one based on the name.
SOURCE: https://github.com/geldata/gel/blob/master/docs/reference/reference/edgeql/insert.rst#2025-04-16_snippet_6

LANGUAGE: edgeql
CODE:
```
with module people
select (
    insert Person {
        name := "Åukasz Langa", is_admin := true
    }
    unless conflict on .name
    else (
        update Person
        set { is_admin := true }
    )
) {
    name,
    is_admin
};
```

